  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6772.16 sitting right between the max negative gamma at 6770 (-39.8B) and positive gamma at 6800 (+45.2B), dealers are likely modest buyers here as spot hovers near amplifying gamma territory. The PIN regime with 6815 flip strike means dealers will aggressively sell any push toward 6800-6815 resistance while providing buying support if we test 6765-6770 negative gamma zones. Watch 6770 as the critical fulcrum - a break below triggers dealer selling into 6765, while a reclaim of 6785-6790 should face heavy resistance from dealer hedging flows.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to get pinned between 6770-6800 with choppy mean-reverting action.",
